====Usage notes====
* For Min Nan, Taiwan's Ministry of Education recommends {{zh-l|*个}} for the general classifier ''ê'' and {{zh-l|*的}} for the possessive particle ''ê'', reserving {{zh-l|*個}} for the month classifier ''kò''.
* For Hakka, Taiwan's Ministry of Education recommends {{zh-l|个}} for the possessive particle.
* In Cantonese, when used for "yuan/dollar", {{lang|zh|個}} is usually only used when followed by cents.

